<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://api.dsapsol.com/favicon.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oleo+Script:wght@400;700&family=Pacifico&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <title>Anotomy MUSEUM</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'poppins';
        }

        :root {
            --prime: <%=direction %>
        }

        .about-most-outsider {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: auto;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 20px;
            flex-direction: var(--prime);
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            padding-right: 40px;
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-text h1 {
            color: #343a40;
            font-size: 48px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-text h1 span {
            color: #0cc0df;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .about-text p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .about-text p strong {
            color: #343a40;
        }

        .about-text .cta-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #f36f45;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .about-text .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: #357ab8;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 1000px;
            max-height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-top: 33px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .about-text {
                padding-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .about-image {
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .about-text h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            .about-text p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .about-text .cta-btn {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }

        .unique-img-section {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* Pure white background */
            text-align: center;
            /* Centering the images */
        }

        /* Styling for the custom row container */
        .custom-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            /* Adds spacing between columns */
        }

        /* Styling for each column */
        .custom-col {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 23%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Styling for the images */
        .image-item {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            /* Fixed height for the images */
            object-fit: cover;
            /* Ensures images cover the area without stretching */
            border-radius: 12px;
            /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            /* Subtle shadow for depth */
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            /* Smooth transition for hover */
        }

        /* Hover effect on images */
        .image-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            border: 1px solid #0cc0df;
            /* Slight zoom effect */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            /* Stronger shadow on hover */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .custom-col {
                max-width: none;
            }

            .custom-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../../common/header') %>
        <div class="about-most-outsider">
            <div class="about-container">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h1><span>ANATOMY MUSEUM</span></h1>
                    <p>The <b>Anatomy Museum</b> at IUK is a center of learning, featuring a diverse collection of
                        anatomical
                        specimens
                        and models. It offers hands-on learning experiences for students, reinforcing theoretical
                        knowledge and
                        supporting faculty research. Additionally, the museum promotes health awareness and sparks
                        curiosity
                        about the human body through outreach programs and exhibitions. Serving as a beacon of
                        education, it
                        empowers future medical professionals to make impactful contributions to healthcare.</p>
                    <a class="cta-btn" href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/anatomy_main.JPG" alt="Image 1" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="unique-img-section">
            <div class="custom-row">
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/anotomy1.png" alt="Image 1" class="image-item">
                </div>
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/anotomy2.png" alt="Image 2" class="image-item">
                </div>
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/anotomy3.JPG" alt="Image 3" class="image-item">
                </div>
                <div class="custom-col">
                    <img src="https://api.dsapsol.com/anotomy4.JPG" alt="Image 4" class="image-item">
                </div>
            </div>
            <%- include('../../common/footer') %>
        </section>
</body>

</html>